{"tid":1631172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日後遊行方式改善方法 不分化 不割蓆","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:09.000Z","uid":311678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2fcfc8be96abd850c491b3d5b885c9dd699e6765","tid":1631172,"uid":311678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港得3萬警力</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">如我地遍地開玩就可減少損傷和減少手足被捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警力根本不能同時多區捕捉<br />\n但集中係一區只會被大圍捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">在民主運動沒有大台的情況下 </span></strong></span><br />\n無需再集結拉banner 只需各區開花，開花就快閃，捉都無得捉<br />\n<br />\n以家集結同一地點 黑警可以停黨鐵，Check巴士去拉人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地應改變遊行策略不再集結<br />\n應要遍地開花<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n我地係要盡快令美國民主法案通過<br />\n令政府無所適應<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家要學習冷靜</strong><br />\n熱血沸騰係好，但不能過火，<strong>以免失民心</strong><br />\n最緊要係歷史會有重影<br />\n香港人 反抗<br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可 <br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrxrMLs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrxrMLs.jpg&h=5e57d66e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"68975d8955462c9bfc214c3ca1234f2cf94f5def","tid":1631172,"uid":109063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"3207e35c007bc1d3549bfc6ffd9aed976cb4e689","tid":1631172,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6f215b5d0fcaa39254943c56ddf588af300d47d7","tid":1631172,"uid":75308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite